high_descs: Turn around, then walk to the counter on your right.
Pick up the tan bottle from between the sinks.
Look towards the cabinet underneath the sink on the right.
Place the bottle in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a bottle in a cabinet.

high_descs: Pick up the lotion on the counter between the two sinks.
Put the lotion in the cabinet under the sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle of lotion in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick up the bottle of soap.
Open the rightmost cabinet and put the soap inside.
anns.task_desc: Put the soap in the right cabinet.
